e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:43:28.000Z","msg":"因為上帝想食咸水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c6a2c342ce0bbb45f5339954d580a1721b881d","tid":785470,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"因為鹹魚翻生 搞到個海變鹹"},{"pid":"ad4fe948a1c7292f4cc321b8251d2ef774bed462","tid":785470,"uid":72465,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正經答<br />\n<br />\n講講海水 D 鹽邊度嚟<br />\n其實係來自石頭表面嘅礦物質<br />\n<br />\n一般嘅雨帶有溶化嘅 CO2 成為 H2CO3 ，帶有微酸性 (pH ~ 5.6)<br />\n落雨嘅時候帶有微酸嘅雨侵蝕石頭表面嘅礦物質成為離子 (ion)<br />\n含離子嘅雨最終會流落海<br />\n雖然大部分離子都會被生物吸收<br />\n少部分離子會一直留喺海入面一路累積<br />\n其中兩隻遺留最多嘅離子係 NA+ 同 Cl-，佔 90%<br />\nNA+ 同 Cl- 結合就係海水入面嘅鹽<br />\n<br />\n利申：小學雞解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13de6383568608900e8104356ba58b888f70524","tid":785470,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09c6a2c342ce0bbb45f5339954d580a1721b881d","tid":785470,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"因為鹹魚翻生 搞到個海變鹹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鹹魚唔會係個海入面"},{"pid":"fb73b3c6411035d6e30f28bc374ecc21b22f9a69","tid":785470,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:29:17.000Z","msg":"因為海水有咸既屬性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd69c3c31213c994279a166903b2a48a6b18e68a","tid":785470,"uid":159444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a634bdc80e323d4d4bb119d17ed50aa41b94f25d","tid":785470,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb0ec33f1d587898618717ed47ddf54bb5943345","tid":785470,"uid":150881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a74b9326578e2d1af2b6bd19986a362a4f9b